JOHANNESBURG – It is well-known that international reality shows are scripted and now fans of Mzansi Magic’s reality TV show Yim'Lo have accused the show's creators of paying people "to lie" on television. In the most recent episode, Sibusiso confessed to his girlfriend and family that he is "cross-dresser." Sibusiso’s revelation left fans in doubt, with many saying the show is scripted. Sibusiso's girlfriend Mbali took the confession with a pinch of salt. After many questions and some laughter, Sibusiso’s family agreed that they will accept him as he is. eNCA